    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好体验你人生中最放松的公路旅行了吗？你从遥远的海滩醒来，驾驶标志性的面包车穿越无尽的程序生成景观，享受一路的风景与旅程。没有截止日期，没有任务压力，没有拯救世界的责任：只有你、一辆面包车、一只猫，还有一条充满美景、有趣人物与宁静的无尽公路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/dea421fd1342c930dc14e60ea6873c48.poster.avif?t=1770915155\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/dea421fd1342c930dc14e60ea6873c48.webm?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/dea421fd1342c930dc14e60ea6873c48.mp4?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>路上有什么等待着你？</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/d4ee92700ea118a10f115d3f1f21498f.poster.avif?t=1770915155\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/d4ee92700ea118a10f115d3f1f21498f.webm?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/d4ee92700ea118a10f115d3f1f21498f.mp4?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽旅程：</strong> 每次旅行可持续任意时间，地图是程序生成的，并包含加油站、商店、瞭望塔和可以结交的新朋友。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三种模式：</strong> 剧情模式讲述温馨的友谊与失落；禅意模式提供每次都不同的旅程；后台模式则可在你放松时继续行驶。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/4964fdd629cc487366119ce07d7a94f5.poster.avif?t=1770915155\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/4964fdd629cc487366119ce07d7a94f5.webm?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/4964fdd629cc487366119ce07d7a94f5.mp4?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式驾驶：</strong> 坐进驾驶座，转动钥匙，松开手刹启程。下雨时开雨刷，调节收音机，电池没电时可以推车启动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可自定义的家：</strong> 用油漆、贴纸和装饰品来美化车内外空间。你可以和猫咪一起在路上生活 —— 是的，猫咪可以撸！别的动物也可以！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/2da0e66c05ae91b8286589217910d191.poster.avif?t=1770915155\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/2da0e66c05ae91b8286589217910d191.webm?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754250/extras/2da0e66c05ae91b8286589217910d191.mp4?t=1770915155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lo-Fi音乐：</strong> 听 Rosentwig、Purrple Cat、Sage Nine、Marlon Schettert 等艺人的放松音乐，也可以制作自己的播放列表伴你上路！</p></li></ul>",
